00206 #define LBX86_EXT(oper) ((Lbx86_Ext_Fields *)(oper->ext))

00208 #define LBX86_SEG_OVR(oper) (LBX86_EXT(oper)->seg_ovr_popval & 0xF)
00209 #define LBX86_POPVAL(oper) ((LBX86_EXT(oper)->seg_ovr_popval >> 4) & 0xF)
00210 #define LBX86_ENCODE_SEG_OVR_POPVAL(seg_ovr, popval) ((char)((popval << 4) | \
00211                                                              (seg_ovr & 0xF)))
00212 
00213 #define LBX86_EXTRACT_GENOPC(popc) ((int)(((unsigned)(popc)) >> 4))
00214 #define LBX86_GENOPC(oper) (LBX86_EXTRACT_GENOPC(oper->proc_opc))
00215 #define LBX86_EXTRACT_VARIANT(popc) ((int)(((unsigned)(popc)) & 0xF))
00216 #define LBX86_VARIANT(oper) (LBX86_EXTRACT_VARIANT(oper->proc_opc))
00217
